beverages and making ice in the summer.</p>

<p>Every environmentally conscious user will be extremely happy
with the fridge''s A+ energy efficiency rating. In addition, the fridge''s quiet
operation rules out any bothersome noise when set up in small one-bedroom
apartments.</p>

<p>Another great feature of the Klarstein fridge is its compact
size, making it the perfect fit for any home.</p>

<p><b>Requirements in accordance with the EU Energy Efficiency
Labelling Regulations Nr. 1060/2010:</b></p>

<p><b>Energy efficiency class: </b>A+ (on a scale from A+++ (highest)
