the basis of testing over a 24-hour period. Actual energy consumption can
depend on use and location of the device).</p>

<p><b>Cubic capacity of storage space: </b>114 litres</p>

<p><b>Cubic capacity of freezer compartment: </b>12 litres</p>

<p><b>Climate class:</b> N</p>

<ul><li>The
climate class ''expanded temperate zones'' bears the symbol ''SN'' for an average
ambient temperature of 10 to 32˚C</li></ul><ul><li>The
climate class ''temperate zones'' bears the symbol ''N'' for an average ambient
temperature of 16 to 32˚C</li></ul><ul><li>The
climate class ''subtropical zone'' bears the symbol ''ST'' for an average ambient
temperature of 16 to 38˚C</li></ul><ul><li>The
climate class ''tropical zone'' bears the symbol ''T'' for an average ambient
temperature of 16 to 43˚C</li></ul>







<p><b>Noise emission in dB(A) re 1 pW: </b>39dB – measured according
